<HL>
   Who's News:
   Berman, Citing Personal Considerations,
   Resigns at U.S. Subsidiary of Nomura
   ----
   By Michael R. Sesit
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/09/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6
</SO>
<CO>
   J.NOM WNEWS
</CO>
<MS>
FINANCIAL (FIN)
</MS>
